embeds.title: :thought_balloon:  Ideals
embeds.description:
Be considerate of what's posted here.
Consider people, active and lurking.
Do not give unsolicited negative feedback.
Avoid reaction gifs and memes.

embeds.title: :placard: User Reports
embeds.description:
If you have an issue with another member, please DM a moderator with the details.
Open conflict in the discord is not allowed unless it's calling out poor behaviour in a constructive manner. Be considerate here, and edit your assumptions.
Conduct in and out of the discord affects people's comfort here and is relevant.

fields.name: :anger:  Toxicity
fields.value:
If someone's proving to be a toxic presence, they will likely be removed from the community. This may take a few forms, different impacts will have varied handling. 
If you feel someone is continually rubbing you the wrong way, or striking out consistently, please reach out and it will be handled considerately.

embeds.title: :pushpin: Channel Embeds
embeds.description:
If you want to contribute to any embed on the discord, you can do so via [github](https://github.com/Interim-Discord/Channel-Embeds/) PRs. 
Please don't hesitate to reach out to <@&914447557688713256> with alterations and additions.
